{
  "text": "MRIs were then segmented into three tissue classes using FSL FAST software 5.0.1 [CITATION_1] . The resulting binary grey matter mask includes voxels where grey matter is the most likely out of the three tissue classes. This mask was then multiplied with the atlas images. Volumes for GM only were again extracted.",
  "correct_citation": {
